Short:	  Experimental Progam to halt Enforcerhitting Processes
Author:   noll@alma.student.uni-kl.de
Uploader: noll@alma.student.uni-kl.de
Type:	  dev/src

EnforcerFreeze can be used to halt a program, that has
produced an Enforcerhit. The hitting task is either decreased
in Priority, or we open a requester about what to do w/ the
Task.

Note that this program is highly experimental.

Source in C and Asm is included.

Requirements:
  Workbench 2.04 or better, 68030, Enforcer

